headline: 3 Reasons to Avoid HAS and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Hasbro trades at $79.12 per share and has stayed right on track with the overall market, gaining 20.2% over the last six months. At the same time, the S&P 500 has returned 16.4%.
